metadata.name: Before Silence
metadata.description:
In a far, it was peaceful. The solitude brings 
the symphony of wind and brighten the surrounding
nature. Before silence, it was chaotic. Miserable
and pain. The life fill with weight of effort and
challenge getting through life journey. Hence the
achievements, the silence of solitude is clear. The
objective been done and the journey is done. Take a
rest now and see how far you've become.
